d:testDescription.p: This test verifies the implementation of the preserveAspectRatio attribute on <image> referencing raster content.

d:operatorScript.p: This is a modified version of the sample file included in the SVG specification. It exercises the various preserveAspectRatio values and uses a general entity definition in order to make reading of the SVG source easier.

d:passCriteria.p: The rendered picture should match the reference image exactly except for variations in the labeling text.

g.text: Test options of preserveAspectRatio on an image element
